verbose_text: It is also noteworthy that the overexpression of a degradation resistant mutant of IkappaBalpha (i.e. IkappaBalphaincrementN) preserves the levels of MyHC in C2C12 myotubes in response to both TNF-alpha and TWEAK suggesting that the activation of classical NF-kappaB pathway predominately mediates the degradation of MyHC in response to both these cytokines [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
